                    <note xml:lang="en" type="description" source="#bib126-4">In hagiography: Constantine was a Bishop of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/78">Edessa</placeName> who may be commemorated in the martyrology of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2282">Rabban Saliba</persName>.</note>
